    public class HelpInline
extends InlineLabel
    HelpInline is a form help text widget.

    HelpInline can include text only.

    UiBinder Usage:

     <b:HelpInline>any text</b:HelpInline>

    Since:
    2.0.4.0
    Author:
    ohashi keisuke
    See Also:
    Controls, HelpBlock, Bootstrap documentation
